rating_comment:
The place is far from NJP railway station approximately 5 km.
But the stay is value of money.
location is good. Size of room is also very good. Cleanliness is superb.
In nut shell the host is very cooperative.

everything was as listed. the only issue was the water in bathroom and no electricity backup. Water in bathroom taps was literally yellow and when we reported, he mentioned that 'thats how it comes in the area'.
Otherwise it value for money.
